OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784875679
OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FThe UK "stands ready 24/7 to defend
OL,7,Fitself", the government has said,
OL,8,Fafter Iran claimed Britain would "bear
OL,9,Fresponsibility" for allowing the US to
OL,10,Fuse British bases.
OL,12,FIt comes after Iran's Ministry of
OL,13,FForeign Affairs (MFA) accused the
OL,14,Fgovernment of "complicity in the crime
OL,15,Fof aggression and war crimes" by
OL,16,Fallowing the US to carry out "unlawful
OL,17,Fattacks".
OL,26,@nD@HOUoD@GO]pD@bOUqD@OO]vD@OOUwD@]O]xD@
OL,26,A^OUyD@HO]
