OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784875679
OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FWhile the government has refused to
OL,7,Ftake part in offensive campaigns
OL,8,Fagainst Iran, it has allowed the US to
OL,9,Flaunch defensive strikes from British
OL,10,Fbases hosting American personnel.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the MFA said that
OL,13,Fanyone who supports "military
OL,14,Faggression against Iran will bear
OL,15,Fresponsibility for the consequences
OL,16,Fand repercussions of its decision".
OL,18,FUS President Donald Trump has carried
OL,19,Fout 13 consecutive nights of strikes
OL,20,Fagainst targets in Iran, indicating
OL,21,Fpotential further escalation.
OL,26,@uD@UOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
