OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784875679
OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,F"This includes through operating a
OL,7,Flayered approach to air and missile
OL,8,Fdefence, provided by Royal Navy,
OL,9,FBritish Army and Royal Air Force
OL,10,Fassets equipped with a range of
OL,11,Fadvanced capabilities, working closely
OL,12,Fwith our Nato allies.
OL,14,F"The UK's approach to the conflict
OL,15,Fremains the same ` we are committed to
OL,16,Fdefending our people, our interests
OL,17,Fand our allies, acting in accordance
OL,18,Fwith international law and not getting
OL,19,Fdrawn into the wider conflict."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@_O]
