OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIran's comments also come after the
OL,12,Fgovernment moved to designate Iran's
OL,13,FIslamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,14,F(IRGC) a threat to national security.
OL,16,FThose carrying out acts of sabotage on
OL,17,Fbehalf of the group will face life
OL,18,Fimprisonment.
