OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FIt follows a series of arson attacks
OL,7,Fin London earlier this year and a
OL,8,Fdouble stabbing in Golders Green.
OL,10,FUS Central Command said the 13th night
OL,11,Fof strikes on Iran, which began late
OL,12,Fon Thursday, were designed to "further
OL,13,Fdegrade Iran's ability to threaten
OL,14,Fcivilian mariners and commercial
OL,15,Fvessels transiting regional waters" as
OL,16,Fthe two countries wrestle for control
OL,17,Fof the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@tD@_OUwD@cO]
