OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784875679
OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FExplosions were heard in Bandar Abbas
OL,7,Fand Qesham on the coast, according to
OL,8,FIranian state media, as well as
OL,9,Ffurther north in Andimeshk and
OL,10,FOmidiyeh.
OL,12,FAnnouncing the end of the latest
OL,13,Fstrikes, US Central Command said
OL,14,FIranian military command centres,
OL,15,Fdrone storage facilities,
OL,16,Fcommunication networks, coastal
OL,17,Fsurveillance sites and maritime
OL,18,Fcapabilities had been targeted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
