OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784875679
OL,3,CUK 'ready to defend itself' after Iran
OL,4,Ccriticises US using British bases
OL,6,FTheir statement said the Strait of
OL,7,FHormuz "remains open for transit
OL,8,Fdespite recent attacks from Iran's
OL,9,FIslamic Revolutionary Guard Corps".
OL,11,FTrump said on Thursday that he would
OL,12,F"hold Iran responsible" for attacks on
OL,13,Fshipping by the Houthis in Yemen and
OL,14,Fthe US would seize Iranian assets to
OL,15,Fcover the cost of damaged ships.
OL,17,FIran's foreign minister Seyed Abbas
OL,18,FAraghchi described such an act as
OL,19,F"incendiary".
